{
  "id": 5577,
  "name": "Crimson Moon’s Semblance",
  "desc": "<p>A keen-edged weapon, luster dazzling as the crimson moon. It is said that an ancient dynasty once regarded it as a ritual object that could bridge two worlds, but none still remember the beliefs and ceremonies of that bygone age.</p>",
  "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/22/35428890/ce91a453b9a942c9ab20df0f62caa033_4944089408609115680.png",
