                  "<p>Polearm</p>"
                ]
              },
              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Secondary Attributes",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>Grants a Bond of Life equal to 25% of Max HP when a Charged Attack hits an opponent. This effect can be triggered up to once every 14s. In addition, when the equipping character has a Bond of Life, they gain a <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">12%/16%/20%/24%/28%</span> DMG Bonus; if the value of the Bond of Life is greater than or equal to 30% of Max HP, then gain an additional <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">24%/32%/40%/48%/56%</span> DMG Bonus.</p>"
                ]
              },
              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Version Released",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>4.6</p>"
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
